{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Base","content":["Preheat oven to 180°C. Grease and line a baking dish (30 x 20 cm) with baking paper and set aside.","Place butter into mixing bowl and melt <nobr>2 min\/50°C\/speed 1<\/nobr>, or until butter has melted.","Add flour, sugar and coconut and mix <nobr>10 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula, then repeat mixing <nobr>10 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>. Transfer into prepared tin and press down to form a base.","Bake for 10 minutes (180°C). Set base aside to cool in tin (approx. 1 hour)."]},{"title":"Caramel filling","content":["Place condensed milk, butter and golden syrup into mixing bowl and cook <nobr>20 min\/100°C\/speed 3<\/nobr>, placing simmering basket instead of measuring cup onto mixing bowl lid.","Pour caramel filling mixture over cooled base in tin, then bake for a further 10 minutes (180°C) then set aside."]},{"title":"Topping","content":["Place chocolate into mixing bowl and grate <nobr>5 sec\/speed 8<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add butter and melt <nobr>2 min 30 sec\/50°C\/speed 2<\/nobr>, or until butter has melted.","Pour chocolate mixture over caramel filling, then sprinkle with sea salt flakes and set aside to cool. Place into refrigerator for approx. 1 hour or until set. Once set, cut into slices and serve."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Base","content":["120 g butter, softened, plus extra for greasing","120 g self-raising flour","120 g soft dark brown sugar","80 g desiccated coconut"]},{"title":"Caramel filling","content":["790 g sweetened condensed milk (2 cans)","120 g butter","100 g golden syrup"]},{"title":"Topping","content":["150 g dark chocolate, broken into pieces (3-4 cm)","20 g butter, softened","sea salt flakes, for sprinkling"]}],"id":"r77121","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-UlpEUJ-XG8E\/XZWqGGEtqvI\/AAAAAAAAfTE\/oYQUfOUNaAQJKf0tPBPYFDYFqUCj-H61wCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_CALed1jH4uvkpazx.png","title":"Salted caramel slice","publishedAt":"2014-07-22T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"3 g","fat":"15 g","uom":"per 1 slice","carbohydrates":"33 g","calories":"1203 kJ \/ 286 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking paper, baking dish (30 x 20 cm), oven, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["For a more traditional caramel slice or if you are making this for children, omit the sea salt flakes at the end."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","2h 30m","24 slices"]}